{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_019VPLQCFX6QdvAtNMgEaPcK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issues clearly:\n\n1. **`/app` vhost**:\n   - `ops-user` has full permissions (`.*`, `.*`, `.*`) on `/app` — this violates the scoping requirement\n   - `app-user` has empty configure permission (`''`, `.*`, `.*`) — the configure permission is broken (empty string means it can't configure anything)\n\n2. **`/ops` vhost**:\n   - `ops-user` has NO permissions on `/ops` — this is the broken part, ops-user can't connect\n   - `app-user` correctly has no access to `/ops`\n\nThe fixes are straightforward: remove `ops-user`'s cross-vhost access to `/app`, grant `app-user` full permissions on `/app`, and give `ops-user` full permissions on `/ops`.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":974,"cache_read_input_tokens":30780,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":974},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2939e2a2-773c-4ae4-b64b-9d1f2e2df113","uuid":"410a095c-2ad7-477d-a7df-4f9676b3666e","request_id":"req_011CcMSauQnwo3pvwuGsmqxA"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_019VPLQCFX6QdvAtNMgEaPcK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issues are clear:\n- `app-user` on `/app`: configure is empty (broken) — needs `.*`\n- `ops-user` on `/app`: full permissions, but should have **none** (cross-vhost leak)\n- `ops-user` on `/ops`: **no permissions at all** — needs full grant\n\nFixing all three:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":974,"cache_read_input_tokens":30780,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":974},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2939e2a2-773c-4ae4-b64b-9d1f2e2df113","uuid":"68ee7185-c780-4f3c-b192-c99845199117","request_id":"req_011CcMSauQnwo3pvwuGsmqxA"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_019VPLQCFX6QdvAtNMgEaPcK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01HLDnhZQRV7ZKN3ragn4q2b","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"NS=\"karma-rabbitmq-full-lifecycle-01-2026-2e2d3162-cluster-a\"\n\n# Fix app-user on /app: set full configure/write/read\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /app app-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\"\n\n# Remove ops-user from /app entirely (cross-vhost violation)\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl clear_permissions -p /app ops-user\n\n# Grant ops-user full permissions on /ops\nkubectl -n $NS exec rabbitmq-0 -- rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /ops ops-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\"","description":"Fix all three permission issues"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":974,"cache_read_input_tokens":30780,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":974},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2939e2a2-773c-4ae4-b64b-9d1f2e2df113","uuid":"337fcb2e-c2af-4419-9e99-32be0487fb8d","request_id":"req_011CcMSauQnwo3pvwuGsmqxA"}
